notes: Exceptions return a value that can be handled by the program.
A stack trace is a sequence of function calls that lead to where an error occurred.
Warnings don't necessarily break a program but may not be apparent.
Strict mode restricts the programmer from writing sloppy code that would otherwise result in an exception or warning
You can check for browser support of a particular api by checking if it exists and then calling it.
Errors include: EvalError, RangeError, ReferenceError, SyntaxError, TypeError, URIError, InternalError
